  <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
     id="ID.00014"
     xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
     Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
     rolemaps-to="P"
    >
   <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>The hidden version declares the label but doesn’t print anything. The next 5 continues to count with the next number. With 4 the label can be used, of course.
  </text>
 </text-unit>
